 libnss3, libgbm1, libasound2t64, libnotify4, libgtk-3-0t64,
 libglib2.0-0t64, libx11-6, libxext6, libdbus-1-3,
 libsecret-1-0, xdg-utils
Description: Level Designer Toolkit — modern 2D level editor
 LDtk is a free, open-source (MIT) 2D level editor for game developers,
 built around tile layers, auto-tiling rules, entities, and a clean JSON
 (.ldtk) export consumed by LibGDX, Godot, Unity, raylib, Heaps and more.
 .
 This package vendors the upstream Linux AppImage (an Electron application)
 to /opt/ldtk and provides an `ldtk` launcher, desktop entry, and icon.
